== 政治行为 ==
[[File:Anjelica_Huston1.JPG|thumb]]2007年Anjelica带领了一个由{{link-en|美国对缅甸活动|U.S. Campaign for Burma}}及人权行动中心组织的信件联名活动。该信件最终有超过25名娱乐业名流签名并递交给[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]，要求他对促使[[缅甸|缅甸]]释放[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]得主[[昂山素季|昂山素季]]作出积极性的个人努力<ref>United States Campaign for Burma. [http://www.uscampaignforburma.org/index.html ''Hollywood: UN Should Act on Burma''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uscampaignforburma.org/index.html |date=20071012233504 }}. United States Campaign for Burma's homepage, 2007年9月6日</ref>。

Anjelica私人捐助了两千[[美元|美元]]给[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]政治[[候选人|候选人]][[约翰·克里|约翰·克里]]和Dick Gephardt。

2012年，安杰丽卡为[[善待动物组织|善待动物组织]]（People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals，简称PETA）录制了一段公益广告，呼吁好莱坞的同僚们不要再在电影、电视及广告中使用猿猴类动物进行表演<ref>Ken Wheaton, "[http://adage.com/article/special-report-super-bowl/peta-anjelica-huston-careerbuilder-chimp-ad/232401/ PETA, Angelica Huston Go After CareerBuilder for Chimp Ad] {{Wayback|url=http://adage.com/article/special-report-super-bowl/peta-anjelica-huston-careerbuilder-chimp-ad/232401/ |date=20160304094822 }}," AdAge.com, 2012-1-27</ref>。晚些时候，善徒动物组织将她评为2012年年度人物<ref>Marc Malkin, "[http://www.eonline.com/news/374549/smash-s-anjelica-huston-named-peta-s-2012-person-of-the-year Smash's Anjelica Huston Named PETA's 2012 Person of the Year] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/374549/smash-s-anjelica-huston-named-peta-s-2012-person-of-the-year |date=20210226152205 }}," eonline.com, 2012-12-28</ref>。

